title: BBQ Pork Fillet Wrap | Aaron Craze's Street Food
description:
Aaron's back on the channel just like you asked for Food Tubers! This time he's got a great street food recipe using pork fillet, sesame seeds, homemade roti wrap and a sweet & spicy Chinese glaze. Stoke up the BBQ and get cookin'!

What's your favourite thing to put in a wrap guys? Got any great street food suggestions? Let us know in the comments box below.
